It is an image processing processing core which handles loading, editing and storage of images using OpenCV and NumPy.
It facilitates all the processing of images with openCV and NumPy.
It loads pictures as well as archives the original and current photo.
It uses image filters like grayscale, blur and edge detect.
It alters the brightness and contrast of the images.
It flips the images by 90 deg, 180 deg and 270 deg.
It flips the image in horizontal and vertical way.
It downsizes images with custom size.
It stores pictures in the form of BGR to be consistent in processing.
It restores the safe copy image in support of undo and redo.
It follows encapsulation and modular method design.
